{"tid":1537632,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"to 各位好攰好傷心好無助既戰友","createTime":"2019-09-04T03:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:19:07.000Z","uid":292497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12a60fe585597774f41137e6a3b67ae6810aac7a","tid":1537632,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月大家都好攰好沮喪好無助仲有唔少手足有尋死既諗法/已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好攰好無助好撚嬲 我相信前線既人/學生可能比我更加無助更嬲<br />\n但千祈唔好諗尋死..人生在世仲有好多野要做<br />\n我地仲要係煲底見面架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果覺得攰既我有套電影推介比大家 -- Darkest Hour黑暗對峙<br />\n邱吉爾當時面對國內主和派既壓力同埋面對納粹呢個咁強大既敵人都無退到最後獲得勝利<br />\n我地都唔可以放棄我相信我地面對ChiNazi都會嬴到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jnmq3iW45xE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Djnmq3iW45xE&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3Kd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=b71e3aff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jnmq3iW45xE</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nWE SHALL NEVER SURRENDER!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"c3c4655c5dae54cfde5bcb93267f6c1fb32194fb","tid":1537632,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:53:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/p